{"tid":1368641,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好比人帶風向互相割𥱊呀","createTime":"2019-07-26T13:58:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T14:50:02.000Z","uid":56394,"like":62,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"3d9b086aa3be8714c95f7c5cb30575408ba71cff","tid":1368641,"uid":56394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:58:38.000Z","msg":"依家連登個風向係和理非同勇武意見又開始分歧<br />\n呢個時勢要急嘅只有政府<br />\n所以我相信依家係<span style=\"color: red;\">一班三毛扮勇武，一班扮和理非</span><br />\n之後就係到互屌侮辱對方<br />\n希望唔好有真心膠落搭<br />\n<br />\n記唔記得我地係點樣一齊捱到依家<br />\n勇武和理非點樣補位<br />\n即使聽日元朗真係發生任何事<br />\n我絕對唔會相信真正香港人會因為元朗有失利而割𥱊<br />\n只要大家仲係團結就唔會有任何所謂失利嘅情況<br />\n<br />\n最後我想講<br />\n我個人係永遠支持任何形式嘅抗爭而且永不割𥱊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"cdd799c81c1317df3105ca97a9fd1b777c83673f","tid":1368641,"uid":198866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:00:14.000Z","msg":"推哩個<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"f5af07a844775eae477cc4fa5d3ed3f092cbf3bd","tid":1368641,"uid":56394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:01:03.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f14837b0d777d42346d39c1aa373676ad25e6f8","tid":1368641,"uid":254880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:02:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f2b5dac7a2afd0a80f2c55c51045754307d53ee","tid":1368641,"uid":245523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:03:07.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<br />\n唔好當勇武係無腦先得㗎 搞咗咁耐 一定熟過班和理非知咩可以做 咩唔可以做<br />\n勇武和理非係缺一不可 唔好咁易比人分化到"},{"pid":"9aa742956ddd2bb04a5ce3f964a1ae68050f8b57","tid":1368641,"uid":133886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:03:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6317534a135ed71de8aadb66735b9ab52bddf29c","tid":1368641,"uid":179225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:05:00.000Z","msg":"不分化！"},{"pid":"75987231c14e3be154cc8f9d9f77f87edb3e24de","tid":1368641,"ui